item.description:
Please note, I have added another session at the same time at Crosby.

This particular session at Dugger Park is for those interested in playing matches. The other session at Crosby is for rallying and practice to develop various tennis skills.

 

Since it's still early in the season, we'll begin with a later start time for now and transition to an earlier start time once it warms up a bit more - eventually 8:30 AM, the same as last year.
item.name: Informal Sunday Tennis @ Dugger, Match Play Session
